Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 迈步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪是闪闪发光的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化为甘霖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西就舍去 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无限广阔的心中蔓延开来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于受伤时刻之外　看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若现在开始映入双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得强大 抓住机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想绝对能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遥远 都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感觉到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配了在遥远天空上的星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以第七星界 为目标展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入了圣天界的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在这里各自寻找自己的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了出身地麾利多村的海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里遇上了在自己出世前的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的把爱得到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三十四话\N古拿玛!再一次的爱!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了…找到爱了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子第一,火子第二!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了…找到爱了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子和海火子也找到爱回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,下一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛,是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找回来,在那一天你失去了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛,失去了的意思到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你说不想去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便等于放弃松明了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟先生也快点去找到爱,拿这个回来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟先生,慢慢行了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你稍微太过嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的地头我们终有一天会收下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘻,被打一身了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛真蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚,你看着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这树一日仍存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的名字也会留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又打架了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是还礼给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你,请你不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当着同伴的面,不好好做过了断不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样继续争斗下去会有什么结果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你,不要再打了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找你很久了,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的首领提出了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一对一的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好做一个了断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是好机会啊,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便可以保护我们的领土了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点的话便没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛求求你,不要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛,你这样也算是男人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人挑起的架,必打是我们的规条啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打架了,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是女人不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样便分出胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是只会令争斗继续下去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想失去你!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点,由莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要来?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去寻找爱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道…由莉亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对救命恩人不是这样的口吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之,突然推倒人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说是救命恩人是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人说的看见了便是死期
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远令人长眠的睡眠雷姆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷姆?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了要感谢我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不喜欢被强迫的谢人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且谢谢你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可以再诚挚一点说多谢的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为是美丽的女人便流口水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不要乱说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是破烂的旅店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临,要住宿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时睡一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我最便宜的房间便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里哪间房都很便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是破旅店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥,你由哪里来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古莉亚,你对客人胡说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起,我女儿说了失礼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?你是我们的客人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识我的女儿的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话你早点说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我去寻找爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星这么罕见吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已一直站在这里几小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才把雷姆认错是另一个人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾把我叫过由莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是又怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看你好像很哀伤的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不可以不要理别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,你打算住多久…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷的话便用那个炉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…把由莉亚还给我!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你爱由莉亚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱由莉亚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然爱了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,为什么不听由莉亚的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因为这样由莉亚才会死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并没有爱由莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚是被你那虚假的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺骗痛苦地死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的爱她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,起来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看见雷姆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?雷姆出现了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有救她的方法吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果得到在镇外沼泽沙洲中盛开的花的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有真实的爱的人进入那沼泽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会有命回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真实的爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个沼泽在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:16:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止架桥过去的、用船过去的人也有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那沼泽是人类自己走进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是过不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有真实的爱的人进入那沼泽是不会有命回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛,不要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由…由莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再干危险的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你爱我的话,便不要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛,你是爱我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你便把那证据给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这里,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊,古拿玛,不要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是爱我的话,便不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你不爱我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和你相识之前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,连知也不想知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会想我自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天胡乱伤害身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这样的生活并不是人生"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…是你告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想永远保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说,不要说!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算那次是最后的,在那次决斗之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算和我的同伴告别的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个只是狡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是狡辩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并没有爱由莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是深深爱过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,现在仍然爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮我,由莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是古拿玛先生替你取沼泽的花来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗,他走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人拥有真实的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是真的爱由莉亚小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到爱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,古拿玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像不太高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你找到失去的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,下一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武一郎,到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父,没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用这剑起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把爱找出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 阴霾的天空里乌云渐渐散去 阳光透过云层照了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人仰望这天空的哪个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眩目的彩虹 即将出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注定出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着光线还没有消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待着明天的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.87,0:23:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的彩虹彼岸里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹出了两个人未来的风

